cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper focuses on using deep learning for landuse mapping, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multiple modalities and the end-to-end trainable model suggest a focus on machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of OpenStreetMap annotations, which falls under graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO) as it involves mapping and navigation.
